title: Darr ka Ghar
subTitle: A man decides to sell his parent's house after their demise. However, he fails to find a suitable buyer as the house is haunted.

title: Ek Aur Bol Bachchan
subTitle: A man and his sister move to a village where a local landlord employs him at his house. Since he pretends to be of a different faith, he faces trouble while keeping up this lie.

title: Athiratha
subTitle: Following a family legacy, a youngster ventures into journalism and investigates a scandal involving a powerful politician. However, his life moves downhill after he is arrested under a false charge.

title: Express Khiladi
subTitle: A pantry worker and a make-up artist develop a romance aboard a runaway train, where they must confront dangerous challenges to save themselves and others.

title: International Khiladi: The Iron Man
subTitle: Amrita's parents get killed. Years later, she falls in love with Aditya only to learn that he was the one who was accused of her parents' murder.

title: Rudhran
subTitle: A man's life takes an unexpected turn when he stumbles upon a criminal network. Determined to bring the truth to light, he sets out to expose the nefarious organisation and protect his loved ones.

title: Captain
subTitle: A captain leads his team of soldiers inside a forest to investigate mysterious disappearances. However, they soon realise that the danger is more than they bargain for.

title: Alluri
subTitle: Iqbal, an aspiring police candidate, embarks on a journey to follow in the footsteps of Alluri, an upright officer, and discovers valuable lessons along the way.

title: Dashing CM Bharath
subTitle: Oxford graduate Bharat assumes his late father's role as chief minister. He strives to reform a corrupt society, but encounters fierce opposition from adversaries.

title: Ek Hi Maqsad
subTitle: Captain Ram is a military commando who rescues Patil, the tourism minister of Karnataka from Jehadi terrorists. Taking a liking for his heroics, Patil engages him to provide security.

title: Ek Hi Maqsad
subTitle: Captain Ram is a military commando who rescues Patil, the tourism minister of Karnataka from Jehadi terrorists. Taking a liking for his heroics, Patil engages him to provide security.

title: Action Blaster
subTitle: Anil Anto, a TV operator, moves to Kochi with his pregnant wife in order to start a new life. There, Anil crosses paths with Darvin, a gangster, post an unfortunate incident.

title: Ek Janbaaz Police Officer
subTitle: Bharat, an honest cop gets transferred to Durgapur which is ruled by Simhadri, a criminal. He decides to teach him a lesson.

title: Sivudu
subTitle: A carefree young man's life is disrupted by rising crime in his locality and when his family faces danger, he decides to fight back.

title: LIE
subTitle: Sathyam and Chaitra meet unexpectedly in their pursuit of making quick money. Soon, after they fall in love, Sathyam encounters Padmanabham, a criminal on the run from the Indian police.

title: Pogaru
subTitle: A local thug stands up against the atrocities committed on common people and fights to secure justice for them, thus earning the public's respect and affection.

title: Naa Saami Ranga
subTitle: A man gains great notoriety in his village for his unmatched strength and brutal nature, which makes him a target of antisocial elements with a ruthless agenda.

title: Garam
subTitle: Varala, a jobless young man, leaves his home to prove himself to his father. However, before achieving his goal, he falls in love with Sameera and tries to woo and save her from gangster Biju.

title: Darbar
subTitle: Aaditya, a high-ranking law enforcement official, sets out to eradicate the city's gangsters. As the events unfold, it becomes clear that his motivations are deeply personal.

title: Inspector Vijay
subTitle: Vijay, an honest police officer, meets Samyukta at a cafe and falls in love with her. However, his life changes when he witnesses a kidnapping and ends up helping a lonely woman, Lavanya.

title: Dangerous Khiladi 2
subTitle: A corrupt minister's daughter finds a diary containing details about a couple's relationship. When the story ends abruptly, she sets out to find the person who wrote it.

title: Kaapa
subTitle: When Anand finds his pregnant wife's name on Kerala's anti-social list alongside other criminals, he sets on a determined mission to clear her name and prove her innocence.

title: Kaapa
subTitle: When Anand finds his pregnant wife's name on Kerala's anti-social list alongside other criminals, he sets on a determined mission to clear her name and prove her innocence.

title: Laila O Laila
subTitle: After his post-graduate studies, Karthik takes a holiday in Europe. On his return journey, he falls in love at first sight with Nandana, and goes to great lengths to win her heart.

title: Time Machine
subTitle: When Elango and Pulivetti find a time machine, they decide to use it for their benefit. While meddling with time, they prevent a gangster's death and this lands them in trouble.

title: Mawali Raaj
subTitle: In order to obtain a family of their own, two young children of two single parents devise a plan to bring them together.

title: Dhruva
subTitle: A committed police officer, Dhruva, uncovers a web of organised crime headed by a scientist, Siddharth Abhimanyu. But when Dhruva tries to build a case against him, he faces many challenges.

title: Siren
subTitle: After serving 14 years in prison, a man is released on parole. As he tries to reconnect with his family, he vows revenge against those who wronged him.

title: Vivegam
subTitle: Ajay Kumar, a former counter-terrorism agent, is called for a special mission. However, he is betrayed by his friends and is accused of extremely treasonous acts.

title: The Family Star
subTitle: Govardhan, a diligent architect, longs for a partner who understands his commitment to his large family. When Indu, a new tenant, moves in, his life starts to unfold in a new direction.

title: Gally Rowdy
subTitle: A young man tries to find a balance between his love interest and friends. Meanwhile, his friends convince him to stay rowdy.

title: Veer Madhakari Iss Sadi Ka
subTitle: Madakari, an honest cop, is killed by the hands of the atrocious Babji. Sathyaraju, who bears an uncanny resemblance to Madakari, takes his place to take care of his daughter amd exact revenge.
